\is1 Introduction
\ip This \bk Sulat of James\bk*, iyan this the nalimud me tambag of James of people migpalintutuu of God. Insulat din this there to langun people nekegsuwey-suwey here of ampew of tane. Miggamit si James of me allegory in order to pegpasabut of people and of pegtambag, eyew egmeupiya the batasan dan and the work ran of tagse aldew. Migpanulu again sikandin of nakalkalasi teaching iling of: faith, peg-correct-correct, peg-antus, pegtahud, good behaviour, good peglalag-lalag, true/correct katuenan from God, and praying.
\ip Migkahi sikandin of kulang the kanta faith ke not egdumaan of work.
\ip The true/correct ngaran of person migsulat here si Hakubu, but si James the igngengaran of me Kastila.
